<L>__{interior soweto police station charge office afternoon}
<A>__{the charge office is sparcely furnished with a long bench along a wall. there is a reception counter with sgt: van zyl in charge. the boys are lined up against a wall. the sergeant stands with a tall blond man with a scar on his chin, captain stolz. the sergeant reads out a name and looks at stolz; if he nods the boy stands aside. after this ritual, the ones that stolz has chosen are marched to a waiting police van and driven away. the others are taken to the cells at the police station, these include jonathan and wellington.}
